data.description: Welcome to this meticulously maintained, move-in-ready brick home in a highly desirable neighborhood! As you enter, you’ll be greeted by exquisite wood tile flooring that extends throughout the entire living areas. The formal living room boasts a large window, offering a charming view of the front yard.  The den seamlessly flows into the kitchen, creating a perfect space for entertaining. Cozy up by the wood-burning brick fireplace in the living area. The kitchen has been tastefully updated with white cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Your convenience is further enhanced with a separate laundry room. This lovely home features three bedrooms and 1.75 bathrooms, ensuring ample space for your family’s needs. Step outside to the expansive covered patio, surrounded by lush shrubs for added privacy, making it the perfect place to unwind and enjoy the outdoors.  Don't miss your chance to make this remarkable property your home.
